<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 60px;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #4CAF50;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.4em;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        span {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff5722;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            display: inline-block;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: block;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }

        .bg-image {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
   
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 40px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1.2em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="bg-image"></div>
        <h1>Thank You!</h1>
        <p>Your generous donation of food will make a significant difference in the lives of those in need. We are incredibly grateful for your kindness and compassion.</p>
        <p>The food you've contributed will be distributed directly to those facing hunger and will help ensure they have a meal on their table.</p>
        <p><span><%=name%></span> from <%=restaurant%> will come to collect the food from your provided location. Your support is invaluable to us and the community.</p>
        <a target="_blank" href="https://mail.google.com/mail/?view=cm&to=<%= name.trim().toLowerCase().replace(/\s/g, '') %>@gmail.com&su=Donation%20Details&body=Dear%20<%=name%>,%0D%0A%0D%0AWe%20are%20grateful%20for%20your%20generous%20donation%20of%20food.%20Your%20kindness%20will%20bring%20hope%20and%20comfort%20to%20many.%0D%0A%0D%0AThe%20food%20you%20have%20contributed%20will%20be%20carefully%20collected%20and%20distributed%20to%20those%20in%20need.%20Your%20support%20ensures%20that%20they%20will%20have%20a%20nutritious%20meal%20on%20their%20table.%0D%0A%0D%0A<%=name%>%20will%20come%20to%20collect%20the%20food%20from%20your%20provided%20location.%20Please%20have%20the%20food%20ready%20for%20collection.%0D%0A%0D%0AThank%20you%20again%20for%20your%20kind%20support.%0D%0A%0D%0AKind%20Regards,%0D%0A<%=restaurant%>">Click Here to Send the Email to <%=name%></a>
        <a href="/">Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
